                                <td style="padding: 4px;" title="Catalyst entry point executed by Starman within the container.">Core PSGI start wrapper.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td style="padding: 4px;"><strong title="deploy.sh: Remote server orchestration script. When triggered, it stops bare-metal host starman.service, backs up running containers (keeping last 2), pulls the new image, starts it, runs health checks, and on failure automatically rolls back to backup and restarts host services, sending log notifications to the admin." style="cursor: help;">deploy.sh</strong></td>
                                <td style="padding: 4px;"><span style="color:#28a745; font-weight:bold;">🟢 Tracked</span></td>
                                <td style="padding: 4px;"><code>./Comserv/script/deploy.sh</code></td>
