                                <td style="padding: 4px;" title="Perl SSH wrapper that compiles, builds, and pushes Docker images to the production server.">Local SSH deployment wrapper.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td style="padding: 4px;"><strong title="Dockerfile: Two-stage container build spec. Stage 1 compiles external CPAN dependencies using native development tools. Stage 2 copies the compiled binaries, sets up the restricted 'comserv' system user, and configures the container to execute Starman in a fully secured, isolated sandbox environment." style="cursor: help;">Dockerfile</strong></td>
                                <td style="padding: 4px;"><span style="color:#28a745; font-weight:bold;">🟢 Tracked</span></td>
